title: Video: Scientists discover 'hog-nosed rat' in Indonesia
text: Scientists discover 'hog-nosed rat' in Indonesia Agence France-PresseOct. 06, 2015. 12:47 PM EST Researchers working in Indonesia have discovered a new species of mammal called the hog-nosed rat...
